Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hsz1665702805717.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsz1665702805717.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsz1665702805717.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hsz1665702805717\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define C Properties\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define C call-out properties for the component implementation\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__section_w56ab1b5b1_w57ab1b5_w58ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__section_rjh_q4f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d390511e56\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__ul_mcm_q4f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__li_d3149e1_d3150e1_d3151e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kdg1665702805860.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdg1665702805860.html\" title=\"Name of the header (.h) file for the C component. If not specified, the default name uo_ComponentName.h is generated. This field is case-sensitive.\">Include File Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__li_d3152e1_d3153e1_d3154e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dhz1665702805929.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dhz1665702805929.html\" title=\"Name of the output (.c) file, up to 16 characters in length. If your operating system does not support 16-character file names, you must specify a compatible file name.\">Output Base File Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__li_d3155e1_d3156e1_d3157e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vtf1665702806001.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtf1665702806001.html\" title=\"Name of the DLL file for this C component implementation. If specified, it is automatically loaded by Uniface when needed.\">DLL Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__li_d3158e1_d3159e1_d3160e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xqt1665702806071.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xqt1665702806071.html\" title=\"Determines whether a context pointer is available for the operations in this C component. Valid values are True or False (default).\">Pass Context Pointer</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__li_d3161e1_d3162e1_d3163e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zcw1665702806140.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zcw1665702806140.html\" title=\"The character set to be used for this C component. Valid values are System Character Set (default), Default Character Set, UTF-8, UTF-16, or UTF-32.\">Character Set Used</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__section_bhk_r4f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d390511e143\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsz1665702805717__p_d6380e1_d6381e1_d6382e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zzx1665702678830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zzx1665702678830.html\" title=\"Use the Signature Editor to create or modify component signatures. Signatures of Uniface components are automatically generated during compilation. Signatures of non-Uniface components can be created or imported.\">Define a Component Signature</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#f